      <para styleclass="Heading1">Simple (Native) Types</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">By simple data types we mean data types that are not primarily used to hold other data, e.g. Objects, Structures, Arrays, etc., that we will see later.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
